:: Grammar Widgets [widget nobr]
<<widget "an">>
<<run console.assert(typeof($args[0]) == "string",`ERROR in a/an widget: invalid argument`)>>
<<set _word = $args[0].toLowerCase()>>
<<switch _word>>
	<<case 'a' 'e' 'i' 'o' 'u'>>
		<<print "an">>
	<<default>>
		<<print "a">>
<</switch>>
<</widget>>


